OL,3,CTrump says Iran doing 'poor job' on
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire teeters
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has said
OL,7,FIran is doing "a very poor job" of
OL,8,Fallowing vessels through the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz as the two-week ceasefire
OL,10,Fappears to become more fragile.
OL,12,F"That is not the agreement we have",
OL,13,Fthe president wrote on Truth Social
OL,14,Fovernight.
OL,16,FThe comment comes as ceasefire
OL,17,Fnegotiations between Iran and the US
OL,18,Fare due to start in Islamabad,
OL,19,FPakistan, over the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
