OL,3,CTrump says Iran doing 'poor job' on
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire teeters
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fspoken to Trump about the need for a
OL,8,F"practical plan" to get shipping going
OL,9,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz, having
OL,10,Fvisited allies in the Gulf for talks
OL,11,Fover the last two days.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@PO]
