OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775894782
OL,3,CTrump says Iran doing 'poor job' on
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire teeters
OL,6,F"The Prime Minister set out his
OL,7,Fdiscussions with Gulf leaders and
OL,8,Fmilitary planners in the region on the
OL,9,Fneed to restore freedom of navigation
OL,10,Fin the Strait of Hormuz, as well as
OL,11,Fthe UK's efforts to convene partners
OL,12,Fto agree a viable plan," Downing
OL,13,FStreet said on Friday.
OL,15,FStarmer told ITV News that there needs
OL,16,Fto be "toll-free navigation" as part
OL,17,Fof the ceasefire, amid reports that
OL,18,FIran wants to charge $1 per oil barrel
OL,19,Fpassing through.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
