OL,3,CTrump says Iran doing 'poor job' on
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire teeters
OL,6,FIran's deputy foreign minister said on
OL,7,FThursday that "the Strait of Hormuz is
OL,8,Fopen", but that any vessel wishing to
OL,9,Fpass through would need guidance from
OL,10,FIranian authorities to do so.
OL,12,F"Anybody who communicates with the
OL,13,FIranian authority has got permission
OL,14,Fto pass," Dr Saeed Khatibzadeh told
OL,15,FITV News International Editor Emma
OL,16,FMurphy.
OL,18,FIsrael to talk with Lebanon
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
