OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775894782
OL,3,CTrump says Iran doing 'poor job' on
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire teeters
OL,6,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,7,FNetanyahu offered a potential boost to
OL,8,Fceasefire efforts in the region when
OL,9,Fhe said he had approved direct talks
OL,10,Fwith Lebanon. The Lebanese government
OL,11,Fhas not made any comments on the
OL,12,Fsupposed talks.
OL,14,FThe announcement came after Israel's
OL,15,Fdeadly attacks on Beirut on Wednesday,
OL,16,Fwhich killed more than 300 people.
OL,18,FTalks between the two countries are
OL,19,Fset to take place on Wednesday,
OL,20,Faccording to reports by the Associated
OL,21,FPress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775894782
OL,3,CTrump says Iran doing 'poor job' on
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire teeters
OL,6,FOn Thursday, Starmer said Israel is
OL,7,F"wrong" to continue its strikes on
OL,8,FLebanon during the ceasefire, saying
OL,9,Fit "should stop" as a "matter of
OL,10,Fprinciple".
OL,12,FWhen asked whether the strikes were a
OL,13,Fbreach of the ceasefire, the prime
OL,14,Fminister said: "It's hard to say that
OL,15,Fthere is a breach when we haven't all
OL,16,Fgot access to all the details of the
OL,17,Fceasefire.
OL,19,F"But let me be really clear about it.
OL,20,FThey're wrong. That shouldn't be
OL,21,Fhappening. That should stop."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
