OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775894782
OL,3,CTrump says Iran doing 'poor job' on
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire teeters
OL,6,FCeasefire as it stands
OL,8,FTrump and Iran agreed to a two-week
OL,9,Fceasefire, with talks to revolve
OL,10,Faround a 10-point plan proposed by
OL,11,FIran, which the president described as
OL,12,F"a workable basis on which to
OL,13,Fnegotiate".
OL,15,FBut there are issues on which both
OL,16,Fsides have previously disagreed, such
OL,17,Fas Iran's right to uranium enrichment
OL,18,Fprogrammes and the presence of US
OL,19,Fmilitary in the area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
